name: Impromptu 5k less than full send
description: After a long day running around, fuelled by an A&W teen burger combo & no warm up, 250m in I thought it’d be fun to go for a 5k pr haha. Was happy to hit sub 22:00 when I saw it was within reach but coulda definitely gone harder/faster if I was prepared, especially through the middle. Definitely didn’t have much of that Jack Coyne savage mentality through this hahaha, for the most part just cruisin’. Pretty strong headwind when running south too. Maybe in December I’ll go for a proper 5k TT. Try to hit sub 21:40. Woo. :)
